# Simple Project Charter

**Project Name:** [Your Project Name]  
**Date:** [Today's Date]  
**Project Manager:** [Your Name]  

## What Are We Building? (1-2 sentences)
[Describe what you're creating in simple terms that anyone can understand]

*Example: We're building a new customer portal that allows clients to view their account information, make payments, and submit support requests online.*

## Why Are We Building It? (The Business Case)
[Explain the problem this project solves or the opportunity it captures]

*Example: Our current customer service team spends 60% of their time answering basic account questions. This portal will reduce those calls by 70% while improving customer satisfaction.*

## Success Criteria (How we'll know we're done)
- [ ] [Specific deliverable 1]
- [ ] [Specific deliverable 2] 
- [ ] [Specific deliverable 3]
- [ ] [Success metric - e.g., "Reduce support calls by 50%"]

