## ðŸ’¡ Pro Tips
- **Keep it simple:** This charter should fit on 1-2 pages
- **Get approval:** Don't start work until stakeholders sign off
- **Update as needed:** Charter can evolve in early project phases
- **Make copies:** Share this with everyone on the project

## Next Steps After Charter Approval
1. [ ] Create detailed project plan
2. [ ] Set up regular team meetings
3. [ ] Begin stakeholder communication plan
4. [ ] Start risk monitoring
5. [ ] Kick off the work!

